company_name: FRIESENKRONE-FEINKOST HEINRICH SCHWARZ & SOHN GMBH & CO. KG
information: The company FRIESENKRONE-FEINKOST HEINRICH SCHWARZ & SOHN GMBH & CO. KG, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1904, which operates in the Fish industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industries. It is based in Marne, Germany.
